sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Your Machine<br/>(Claude CLI)
    participant API as Anthropic API<br/>(api.anthropic.com)
    participant Target as Target Website<br/>(example.com)

    User->>API: POST /v1/messages (prompt + conversation)
    API-->>User: Response: "use WebFetch on example.com"

    Note over User: Claude CLI executes WebFetch locally

    User->>Target: GET https://example.com<br/>User-Agent: Claude-User
    Target-->>User: 200 OK (page content)

    Note over User: Target server sees YOUR IP address

    User->>API: POST /v1/messages (tool result + page content)
    API-->>User: Response: summary of the page
